  "detailed_description": "Time to GOLF is a golf climbing game conceived by an author who has never played golf before.<br><br>While touching the ground or a wall, simply drag the mouse to launch the ball in that direction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/d4e88e1907493ce257100ce25a7af2e1.poster.avif?t=1613660718\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/d4e88e1907493ce257100ce25a7af2e1.webm?t=1613660718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/d4e88e1907493ce257100ce25a7af2e1.mp4?t=1613660718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>On your way up the mountain, you will come into contact with various animals and objects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/af83b1efd1b83918899cf8e34a166d02.poster.avif?t=1613660718\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/af83b1efd1b83918899cf8e34a166d02.webm?t=1613660718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/af83b1efd1b83918899cf8e34a166d02.mp4?t=1613660718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will also experience falls that will make you want to throw the mouse.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/877faca18c22bdef56275552fb7f4b4d.poster.avif?t=1613660718\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/877faca18c22bdef56275552fb7f4b4d.webm?t=1613660718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528880/extras/877faca18c22bdef56275552fb7f4b4d.mp4?t=1613660718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Created under the influence of Pogostuck: Rage With Your Friends.",
